# API Proxy Configuration
# Proxy API requests to the backend (BRH/FastAPI)
# Set BACKEND_URL in Netlify environment variables to your backend URL
# Example: BACKEND_URL=https://your-backend.onrender.com
#
# If BACKEND_URL is not set, API calls will fail gracefully
# Uncomment and update the backend URL when backend is deployed:
#
# /api/* https://your-backend-url.com/api/:splat 200
# /.netlify/functions/api-* https://your-backend-url.com/api/:splat 200

# SPA fallback - must be last
/* /index.html 200
